.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH cmux 1  "cmux " 
.SH NAME
cmux \- Control cmux terminal multiplexer
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcmux\fR [\fB\-\-socket\fR] [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-json\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-color\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Control cmux terminal multiplexer
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-socket\fR \fI<SOCKET>\fR
Path to the cmux socket (overrides discovery)
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output raw JSON responses
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-json\fR
Suppress JSON output for browser commands (browser defaults to JSON)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Verbose output (connection info to stderr)
.TP
\fB\-\-color\fR \fI<COLOR>\fR [default: auto]
Color mode: always, never, auto
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
cmux\-ping(1)
Ping the running cmux instance
.TP
cmux\-identify(1)
Show cmux instance identity (version, platform, pid)
.TP
cmux\-capabilities(1)
List supported socket commands
.TP
cmux\-list\-workspaces(1)
List all workspaces
.TP
cmux\-current\-workspace(1)
Show the current workspace
.TP
cmux\-raw(1)
Send an arbitrary JSON\-RPC method
.TP
cmux\-new\-workspace(1)
Create a new workspace
.TP
cmux\-select\-workspace(1)
Select a workspace by ID
.TP
cmux\-close\-workspace(1)
Close a workspace by ID
.TP
cmux\-rename\-workspace(1)
Rename a workspace
.TP
cmux\-next\-workspace(1)
Switch to next workspace
.TP
cmux\-prev\-workspace(1)
Switch to previous workspace
.TP
cmux\-last\-workspace(1)
Switch to last active workspace
.TP
cmux\-reorder\-workspace(1)
Reorder a workspace
.TP
cmux\-list\-surfaces(1)
List all surfaces
.TP
cmux\-split(1)
Split a surface
.TP
cmux\-focus\-surface(1)
Focus a surface by ID
.TP
cmux\-close\-surface(1)
Close a surface by ID
.TP
cmux\-send\-text(1)
Send text to a surface
.TP
cmux\-send\-key(1)
Send a key event to a surface
.TP
cmux\-read\-text(1)
Read text from a surface
.TP
cmux\-health(1)
Check surface health
.TP
cmux\-refresh(1)
Refresh a surface
.TP
cmux\-list\-panes(1)
List all panes
.TP
cmux\-focus\-pane(1)
Focus a pane
.TP
cmux\-last\-pane(1)
Switch to last focused pane
.TP
cmux\-list\-windows(1)
List all windows
.TP
cmux\-current\-window(1)
Show current window info
.TP
cmux\-layout(1)
Show layout tree
.TP
cmux\-type(1)
Type text into the focused terminal
.TP
cmux\-list\-notifications(1)
List notifications
.TP
cmux\-clear\-notification(1)
Clear a notification
.TP
cmux\-browser(1)
Browser automation (agent primary interface)
.TP
cmux\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
